到"},{"pid":"fe78c5cf294fcbff54faa030963431d1ae62f4ea","tid":525783,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"呢d極端減法比你減到都遲早反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202134bf6f9fc5e1ed6266afed72ebffd40b2ae6","tid":525783,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:23:47.000Z","msg":"做運動啦 哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c652f8a22ef73661e7d5c9d6bb4eba17c6c13d8a","tid":525783,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"減咩脂丫<br />\n你咁為食<br />\n好快打回原型<br />\n你同好多香港男人一樣<br />\n肥想減&gt;極端咁改係食方面&gt;狂做運動&gt;一個月後肚腩無咩大改變&gt;咁辛苦做咩&gt;食返多左&gt;心諗做人最緊要享受&gt;某短時間過左又想減肥"},{"pid":"e16009534c7cccc1d780bdec37fd046a58108ad0","tid":525783,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202134bf6f9fc5e1ed6266afed72ebffd40b2ae6","tid":525783,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:23:47.000Z","msg":"做運動啦 哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"一齊有做開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b194f5fce5bb768405c84e99a1e1c9e524601055","tid":525783,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c652f8a22ef73661e7d5c9d6bb4eba17c6c13d8a","tid":525783,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"減咩脂丫<br />\n你咁為食<br />\n好快打回原型<br />\n你同好多香港男人一樣<br />\n肥想減&gt;極端咁改係食方面&gt;狂做運動&gt;一個月後肚腩無咩大改變&gt;咁辛苦做咩&gt;食返多左&gt;心諗做人最緊要享受&gt;某短時間過左又想減肥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"我做左好耐運動了 唔好衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13241a685d97039e4e0e811ea085d9af719f0da2","tid":525783,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:37:46.000Z","ms